aVAgain, they may have said, "I was forced," but never that it didn't happen.
p43
aVHaving thought that through,
p44
aVI decided denial was not going to be on my agenda;
p45
aVI had bigger things to worry about, to write about, to research,
p46
aVand I moved on.
