p49
aVand two senior scholars \u2014
p50
aVtwo of the most prominent historians of the Holocaust \u2014
p51
aVapproached me and said,
p52
aV"Deborah, let's have coffee.
p53
aVWe have a research idea that we think is perfect for you."
p54
aVIntrigued and flattered that they came to me with an idea
p55
aVand thought me worthy of it,
p56
aVI asked, "What is it?"
