aa(lp119
VThe other thing I found \u2014
p120
aVmany of us have been taught to think there are facts and there are opinions \u2014
p121
aVafter studying deniers,
p122
aVI think differently.
p123
aVThere are facts,
p124
aVthere are opinions,
p125
aVand there are lies.
p126
aVAnd what deniers want to do is take their lies,
p127
aVdress them up as opinions \u2014
p128
aVmaybe edgy opinions,
p129
aVmaybe sort of out-of-the-box opinions \u2014
p130
aVbut then if they're opinions,
p131
aVthey should be part of the conversation.
p132
aVAnd then they encroach on the facts.
