aa(lp134
VI published my work \u2014
p135
aVthe book was published,
p136
aV"Denying the Holocaust: The Growing Assault on Truth and Memory,"
p137
aVit came out in many different countries,
p138
aVincluding here in Penguin UK,
p139
aVand I was done with those folks and ready to move on.
