aa(lp148
VDavid Irving suing me?
p149
aVWho was David Irving?
p150
aVDavid Irving was a writer of historical works,
p151
aVmost of them about World War II,
p152
aVand virtually all of those works took the position
p153
aVthat the Nazis were really not so bad,
p154
aVand the Allies were really not so good.
