aVAnd what is that version?
p202
aVThere was no plan to murder the Jews,
p203
aVthere were no gas chambers,
p204
aVthere were no mass shootings,
p205
aVHitler had nothing to do with any suffering that went on,
p206
aVand the Jews have made this all up
p207
aVto get money from Germany
p208
aVand to get a state,
