aa(lp226
VThe judge found David Irving
p227
aVto be a liar,
p228
aVa racist,
p229
aVan anti-Semite.
p230
aVHis view of history was tendentious,
p231
aVhe lied, he distorted \u2014
p232
aVand most importantly,
p233
aVhe did it deliberately.
p234
aVWe showed a pattern, in over 25 different major instances.
p235
aVNot small things \u2014 many of us in this audience write books,
p236
aVare writing books;
p237
aVwe always make mistakes, that's why we're glad to have second editions:
p238
aVcorrect the mistakes.
