aa(lp246
VBut how did we win?
p247
aVWhat we did is follow his footnotes back to his sources.
p248
aVAnd what did we find?
p249
aVNot in most cases,
p250
aVand not in the preponderance of cases,
p251
aVbut in every single instance where he made some reference to the Holocaust,
p252
aVthat his supposed evidence was distorted,
p253
aVhalf-truth,
p254
aVdate-changed,
p255
aVsequence-changed,
p256
aVsomeone put at a meeting who wasn't there.
