aVIn other words, he didn't have the evidence.
p258
aVHis evidence didn't prove it.
p259
aVWe didn't prove what happened.
p260
aVWe proved that what he said happened \u2014
p261
aVand by extension, all deniers, because he either quotes them
p262
aVor they get their arguments from him \u2014
p263
aVis not true.
p264
aVWhat they claim \u2014
p265
aVthey don't have the evidence to prove it.
