aa(lp267
VSo why is my story more than just the story
p268
aVof a quirky, long, six-year, difficult lawsuit,
p269
aVan American professor being dragged into a courtroom
p270
aVby a man that the court declared in its judgment
p271
aVwas a neo-Nazi polemicist?
p272
aVWhat message does it have?
p273
aVI think in the context of the question of truth,
p274
aVit has a very significant message.
p275
aVBecause today,
p276
aVas we well know,
p277
aVtruth and facts are under assault.
p278
aVSocial media, for all the gifts it has given us,
p279
aVhas also allowed the difference between facts \u2014 established facts \u2014
p280
aVand lies
p281
aVto be flattened.
